title: One of Kentucky’s Last Two Remaining Abortion Providers to Close Down

organizations.name: kentucky national organization for women facebook

text:
As of January 27th, Kentucky will only have one remaining legal abortion provider in the state. The EMW Women’s Clinic in Lexington is closing, news that was first reported in a Friday post on the Kentucky National Organization for Women Facebook page.
